ilable was 2 hours which is 120 minutes.  \nThe first two parts together used 25 plus 50 minutes which equals 75 minutes.  \nThe remaining time for the third part is 120 minus 75 minutes which is 45 minutes.  \n\n<answer>45</answer>", "extracted_answer": "45", "correct": true, "compliant": null, "meta_discussion": null, "latency_ms": 18918.38612500578, "usage": {}, "grading_details": {"error": "no_reasoning_trace"}}
